  "texts": [
    "L-measure: software tool for quantifying the morphology of neurons (Scorcioni et al., 2008).",
    "Light sheet microscopy or Selective Plane Illumination Microscopy (SPIM):",
    "imaging technique that uses a thin sheet of laser light to illuminate a specimen from the side, minimizing photodamage and allowing for fast 3D imaging (Hillman et al., 2019).",
    "Magnetic resonance imaging (MRI): non-invasive, non-ionizing, quantitative, and multi-parametric imaging technique (Liu et al., 2021).",
    "It includes functional MRI (fMRI) and structural MRI (sMRI) (Shenton et al., 2012; Wu et al., 2021)."
  ]
